      action: "Binds synaptic vesicle protein SV2A, modulating neurotransmitter release to prevent seizure propagation; preferred anticonvulsant in renal failure",
      sideEffects: "Drowsiness, dizziness, behavioral changes (irritability, agitation), fatigue, headache",
      contra: "Hypersensitivity to levetiracetam; dose adjustment required in renal impairment (reduce dose based on CrCl)",
