        options: ["I will take this medication until all my UTI symptoms are completely gone","This medication will cure my infection so I may not need the antibiotic","I should expect my urine to turn orange-red and I will only take this for 2 days","I should stop taking my antibiotic once the burning goes away since this medicine is treating the infection"],
        correct: 2,
